The 2022 Vietnam Open (officially known as the Yonex-Sunrise Vietnam Open 2022 for sponsorship reasons) was a badminton tournament which took place at in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam, from 27 September to 2 October 2022 and had a total purse of $75,000.
2022年越南羽毛球公開賽為第17屆越南羽球公開賽，是2022年世界羽聯世界巡迴賽的其中一站，屬於第六級別（超級100賽）賽事。本屆賽事於2022年9月27日至10月2日在胡志明市的Nguyen Du Stadium舉行，並獲得YONEX-SUNRISE贊助，總獎金為7萬5千美元。
